claim.claim-text:
10. The battery system of claim 1, wherein the first circuit board comprises:
a plate;
a first portion of the plate to be attached to the connecting portion;
a second portion of the plate on an opposite side of the first portion and extending in a direction away from the connection portion;
a power receiver provided in the second portion and configured to receive power from the first battery cell through the connector; and
a voltage sensor provided in the second portion and configured to sense a voltage of the first battery cell.
